com.google.api.gax.grpc

Class CallContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.api.gax.grpc.CallContext

  • public final class CallContext
extends Object
    CallContext encapsulates context data used to make an RPC call.

    CallContext is immutable in the sense that none of its methods modifies the CallContext itself or the underlying data. Methods of the form withX, such as withChannel(io.grpc.Channel), return copies of the object, but with one field changed. The immutability and thread safety of the arguments solely depends on the arguments themselves.
